# Editor and version-control metadata
**/.git
**/.github
**/.gitignore
**/.idea
**/.vscode
**/*.swp

# Local environments and package-manager caches
**/.venv*
**/.*-venv*
**/.uv-cache
**/.codex-uv-cache

# Python bytecode and tool caches
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/*.pyd
**/.mypy_cache
**/.pytest_cache
**/.ruff_cache

# Tests, coverage, and build artifacts
**/tests
**/pytest-cache-files-*
**/.coverage
**/coverage.xml
**/htmlcov
**/build
**/dist
**/*.egg-info

# Runtime and local-only state
**/checkpoints
**/logs
**/.env
**/.env.*
